metadata.name: Annette Echikunwoke
metadata.description:
Annette Echikunwoke competes in the Hammer Throw. All athletes receive royalities on all future card transactions.
This campaign is part of a larger vision we have at Zelos to support a more community-driven and independent track and field. Every step of the way athletes are contributing to the livelihood of real athletes, helping them fund their ability to compete while investing in an undervalued steady and untapped market. Fans can invest in their favorite athlete's digital collectible.
